
TweakUI and other Power Toys
	http://www.microsoft.com/ntworkstation/downloads/default.asp

Tab Completion
	HKEY_CURRENT_USER\Software\Microsoft\Command Processor -> 9
	
	add path completion
		create PathCompletionChar key -> 9
	
	turn completion on in cmd session or from Run
		'cmd /f:on'
			C+F file completion
			C+D	dir completion


Prompt Here
	Make a new association for the Folder type of 'cmd.exe'


